view from view gives i32:
  let cells be buffer of 6 i32 filled with 0
  for each index i of cells:
    cells at i becomes i
  let outer be view of cells from 1 for 4
  let inner be view of outer from 1 for 2
  let total be 0
  for each index i of inner:
    total becomes total plus inner at i
  total

main gives i32:
  view from view
